en:
I've been at this for a while now, and it
doesn't look like I'll be done any time soon.

I get to see a lot of people pass by while I'm
here digging for days.

I can't wrap my head around one thing,
though..
Why is it that people refer to me as "Shovel Guy"?
It's only been a few days since I've started!

The one nickname I REALLY don't understand
is "Shovel Night".
Where do they get that from?!

Don't tell me...
Is it because I shovel at night, too?
